First, the master problem aims to find the optimal day-ahead scheduling strategy for the IES based on a known worst-case scenario probability distribution, and the master problem can be expressed as:37minaTx+bTy0+WW≥∑k=1Kpk(m)(bTyk(m)),∀m=1,2,…,n\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
